Friends of Claude.

25:28.000 --> 25:31.100
- Okay.
- Thank you very much.

25:31.100 --> 25:33.400
- Merci beaucoup.
- De rien.

25:36.600 --> 25:38.700
[ Cracks Knuckles ]

25:38.800 --> 25:42.100
## [ Continues ]

25:47.500 --> 25:49.800
[ Liquid Streaming ]

25:58.700 --> 26:03.400
- She ain't here, man.
- I can't believe she'd be
at a dump like this.

26:03.400 --> 26:05.600
[ Scoffs ]
Yeah, she's way too centered.

26:07.900 --> 26:10.900
[ Claude ]
Glad you could come. Enjoy the party.

26:11.000 --> 26:14.400
- Merci.
- Think he's boinkin' her?

26:14.400 --> 26:18.100
Thanks a lot, Brad. I'm gonna go
back to the villa, see if she's there.

26:18.200 --> 26:22.400
- No, no, no, I'll go. You stay here
in case she shows up.
- Would you?

26:22.500 --> 26:25.000
- Yes.
- Thanks. I appreciate it.

26:26.700 --> 26:29.500
[ Metal Squeaking ]

26:40.500 --> 26:42.400
Serafine?

26:42.500 --> 26:45.000
[ Dog Barking ]

26:55.200 --> 26:58.100
Hello?

27:13.100 --> 27:15.700
Hello?

27:17.200 --> 27:20.500
[ Serafine ]
Go away!

27:20.600 --> 27:23.500
Go!

27:26.800 --> 27:29.400
- What are you doing here?
- You're askin' me?

27:29.400 --> 27:31.600
- Please, stay away. Go now.
- Don't you wanna get outta here?

27:31.700 --> 27:35.900
- Just leave me alone.
- Oh, is this some kind
of kinky game or something?

27:37.300 --> 27:39.600
Where are your friends?

27:39.700 --> 27:42.500
- They're at Claude's party
waiting for you.
- Party?

27:42.500 --> 27:44.800
Yeah. You know,
that-- that "Iunar" thing.

27:47.900 --> 27:50.700
Oh, my God! They're in great danger!
Get the key! Over there.

27:50.800 --> 27:52.800
Wait, wait.
What kind of danger?

27:52.900 --> 27:55.900
- Just leave it to me.
- No way. If there's a problem,
I'm coming with you.

27:56.000 --> 27:59.100
- It's much too dangerous, believe me.
- Now hold on a second, hot pants.

27:59.200 --> 28:02.500
There's no way
that I'm gonna--

28:02.600 --> 28:05.200
- ## [ Continues ]
- Bottoms up.

28:05.300 --> 28:07.700
- [ Roars ]
- [ Screams ]

28:09.300 --> 28:11.400
Americans.
You can tell a mile away.

28:11.500 --> 28:14.700
[ Laughing ]

28:22.500 --> 28:24.600
[ Groans ]

28:24.700 --> 28:27.100
[ Coughing ]

28:28.700 --> 28:32.400
- [ Heart Monitor Beeping ]
- [ Heavy Breathing ]

28:38.200 --> 28:41.200
Hello?

28:42.900 --> 28:45.600
Could use a little help
over here?

28:49.700 --> 28:51.900
Thanks.

28:55.200 --> 28:57.300
[ Bicycle Squeaking ]

28:57.400 --> 29:00.200
Wait!

29:00.300 --> 29:02.300
I must go in!

29:02.400 --> 29:05.300
Serafine.
Is Claude expecting you?

29:05.400 --> 29:08.800
- Open the door, quick.
- I'm not sure I can do that.

29:08.900 --> 29:12.200
Would you rather have me
stay out here with you?

29:12.300 --> 29:15.000
No, of course not.

29:22.700 --> 29:24.600
[ Men Chanting ]
No-ha!

29:24.700 --> 29:27.200
No-ha! No-ha!

29:31.100 --> 29:34.000
- We must get out of here quick!
- Serafine.

29:34.000 --> 29:36.700
- What's the matter?
- Do as you're told.

29:39.400 --> 29:41.400
He's mine, Jack.

29:44.100 --> 29:47.000
Your buddy just scored.

29:49.700 --> 29:52.500
[ Grunts ]
Hey. Slow down.

29:57.200 --> 30:01.300
Depuis quand tu laisses
partir mes invites, Jacques?

30:01.400 --> 30:04.000
Viens avec moi.

30:26.400 --> 30:28.900
[ Heavy Breathing Continues ]

30:43.500 --> 30:45.900
Damn!

30:48.400 --> 30:50.300
[ Spits ]

30:55.000 --> 30:56.900
Yes!

31:04.500 --> 31:06.400
Through there, hurry!

31:06.500 --> 31:08.500
- Why? Where are we going?
- [ Panting ]

31:13.500 --> 31:15.900
- [ Shirt Ripping ]
- Whoa.

31:16.000 --> 31:18.200
- You must go before it's too late!
- What?

31:18.300 --> 31:21.000
Now? We just got started.
[ Groans ]

31:23.100 --> 31:25.500
[ Groans ]

31:25.500 --> 31:27.900
I'll never understand women.

31:28.000 --> 31:31.100
- Run! Your life is in danger!
- Really? Why?

31:31.200 --> 31:33.600
- Is Claude your boyfriend?
- [ Groans ] Please, go.

31:33.700 --> 31:36.100
[ Voice Deepens ]
Go. Go.

31:36.100 --> 31:39.200
- Damn it, run!
- Serafine, what's wrong?

31:40.700 --> 31:43.700
- [ Roaring ]
- What are you doin'?

31:43.800 --> 31:46.300
[ Voice Cracking ]
Run! Run for your life, Andy!

31:48.500 --> 31:51.700
## [ Continues ]

31:51.700 --> 31:53.900
[ Roars ]

31:55.600 --> 31:59.000
- [ Laughing ]
- [ Roaring ]

32:05.700 --> 32:08.400
[ Neck Muscles Crack ]

32:10.300 --> 32:13.400
[ Roaring ]

32:19.800 --> 32:22.400
[ Growling ]

32:25.100 --> 32:28.000
[ Bones Crunching ]

32:30.100 --> 32:32.600
[ Roars ]

32:40.800 --> 32:44.000
[ People Screaming ]

32:47.200 --> 32:50.900
- [ Electrical Sparking ]
