33:19.700 --> 33:24.000
Andy? Sounds like the party
is just gettin' started up there.

33:27.300 --> 33:30.000
[ Screaming ]

33:36.800 --> 33:40.200
[ Screaming ]

33:44.200 --> 33:47.500
- Open the door!
- Sorry. Members only.

33:47.600 --> 33:49.900
No scum allowed.

33:51.500 --> 33:53.600
[ Werewolf Growling ]

33:54.500 --> 33:57.100
[ Beeping Continues ]

33:57.200 --> 33:59.800
[ Heavy Breathing Continues ]

34:01.700 --> 34:03.800
[ Low Growl ]

34:07.600 --> 34:09.699
[ Fabric Ripping ]

34:12.100 --> 34:14.800
[ Rapid Beeping ]

34:19.100 --> 34:22.800
Hey. Hey, you okay in there?

34:26.900 --> 34:29.199
[ Low Growl ]

34:34.300 --> 34:36.300
[ Screams ]

34:40.400 --> 34:42.400
[ Roaring ]

35:13.800 --> 35:15.700
Andy?

35:18.700 --> 35:22.100
[ Low Growl ]

35:33.600 --> 35:35.800
- [ Roaring ]
- [ Screaming ]

35:38.200 --> 35:40.000
[ Gasping ]

35:41.100 --> 35:45.000
[ Skin Tearing ]

36:08.300 --> 36:11.300
[ Wolf Howling ]

36:11.400 --> 36:13.300
Brad?

36:19.700 --> 36:21.600
Serafine?

36:27.600 --> 36:31.400
Great. Come to Paris
and check out les drains.

36:35.100 --> 36:37.600
[ Footsteps ]

36:37.700 --> 36:40.200
- Hello?
- [ Low Growl ]

36:42.300 --> 36:45.300
- Hello?
- [ Low Growl ]

36:56.200 --> 36:59.300
[ Roaring ]

37:05.000 --> 37:07.700
[ Screeching ]

37:15.000 --> 37:17.900
Whoa.

37:27.000 --> 37:29.400
[ Screaming ]

37:29.400 --> 37:31.900
[ Grunting ]

37:35.800 --> 37:38.100
- [ Straining ]
- [ Roars ]

37:41.400 --> 37:44.300
[ Grunting ]

37:50.300 --> 37:53.300
[ Wolves Howling ]

38:01.600 --> 38:04.500
[ Birds Twittering ]

38:05.900 --> 38:08.800
[ Insect Buzzing ]

38:22.100 --> 38:25.100
## [ Slow Rap Playing
ln The Distance ]

38:27.700 --> 38:29.700
Serafine?

38:29.800 --> 38:32.700
## [ Continues ]

39:01.600 --> 39:04.100
[ Object Bangs Window ]

39:08.200 --> 39:11.000
[ Banging ]

39:12.900 --> 39:15.100
[ Banging ]

39:22.500 --> 39:25.600
- Hey, what the--
- Shh! Get outta there now!

39:25.700 --> 39:27.900
Wha-- Why?

39:28.000 --> 39:30.400
- There's a mutant in the cellar!
- A what?

39:30.500 --> 39:32.400
That French girl,
she's a freak!

39:32.500 --> 39:34.500
- [ Door Opening ]
- Get outta there, man!

39:34.600 --> 39:36.900
- [ Groans ]
- Andy.

39:38.200 --> 39:41.200
You must rest.
Lie down.

39:41.200 --> 39:44.200
Hey, what happened last night?
How did I get here?

39:44.200 --> 39:47.200
Relax. Let me look
at your leg first.

39:48.700 --> 39:51.300
I was attacked...

39:51.300 --> 39:54.300
by this big, wild dog.

39:54.400 --> 39:59.900
It was huge. It had grande yellow eyes,
beaucoup teeth and--

39:59.900 --> 40:03.200
- Do you have rabies here?
- You don't have rabies.

40:04.400 --> 40:06.400
That's healing pretty fast.

40:06.500 --> 40:09.500
How long have I been here?

40:09.600 --> 40:13.300
Just a few hours.
It's your new metabolism.

40:17.000 --> 40:19.800
- Drink this. You'll feel much better.
- What is that?

40:19.900 --> 40:22.900
- It's all natural.
- Because I hate Clamato.

40:23.000 --> 40:25.200
It tastes... different.

40:25.300 --> 40:28.000
[ Insect Buzzing ]

40:29.900 --> 40:33.000
Wait, something weird
is goin' on here.

40:33.100 --> 40:35.100
- I gotta go.
- Shh.

40:35.200 --> 40:38.000
- My friends. [ Gasps ]
- You mustn't. Please.

40:41.200 --> 40:43.600
This will relax you, no?

40:43.700 --> 40:46.300
I don't get it.

40:46.400 --> 40:49.400
Last time we met,
you threw bricks at me.

40:49.400 --> 40:51.500
Listen.

40:51.600 --> 40:54.700
- You're not the same as you used to be.
- Only since I met you.

40:54.800 --> 40:58.700
Seriously.
There's something I have to tell you,

40:58.700 --> 41:01.500
but you have to promise me
you're not gonna freak out, okay?

41:01.500 --> 41:04.200
- No, I'm a rock.
- Okay.

41:04.200 --> 41:07.400
Um, the injury on your leg,

41:07.500 --> 41:09.500
it was not from a dog.

41:09.500 --> 41:13.400
It was--
[ Sighs ] It was a werewolf.

41:14.900 --> 41:16.900
[ Laughing ]

41:18.000 --> 41:20.100
- Yeah.
- I'm serious.

41:20.200 --> 41:22.300
- And now you have become one too.
- [ Boisterous Laughter ]

41:24.100 --> 41:27.700
Great. Oh, I get it.
I get it.

41:27.700 --> 41:31.500
Not Cinderella.
Little Red Riding Hood now.

41:31.600 --> 41:35.400
Whatever kinky game
you want to play, I am in.

41:35.400 --> 41:37.500
[ Howling ]

41:37.600 --> 41:39.500
- [ Growls ]
- [ Door Opens ]

41:39.600 --> 41:42.100
[ Howling Continues ]

41:42.200 --> 41:45.200
[ Chuckles, Continues Howling ]

41:46.400 --> 41:49.000
[ Baying, Growls ]

41:52.800 --> 41:55.000
[ Low Howling ]

41:55.100 --> 41:57.800
Andy?

41:57.900 --> 41:59.800
Hi.

41:59.900 --> 42:02.500
I was havin' a bad dream,

42:02.600 --> 42:04.600
I guess.

42:04.700 --> 42:07.700
Um--

42:07.800 --> 42:10.900
- Are you feeling better?
- No.

42:11.000 --> 42:15.300
I guess l--
My hangover's doing fine.

42:17.900 --> 42:20.600
You need to relax,
n'est ce pas?

42:21.700 --> 42:23.700
- [ Roaring ]
- [ Screaming ]

42:23.800 --> 42:26.500
[ Gasping ]

42:26.500 --> 42:30.700
Oh, my God!
I thought, uh--

42:30.700 --> 42:33.300
Oh, man. What did they put
in those drinks?

42:33.300 --> 42:37.000
You were hallucinating. It's quite
normal for the transition period.

42:37.100 --> 42:39.900
- Just try to relax, okay?
- "Transition period"?

42:40.000 --> 42:41.900
Mm-hmm.

42:42.000 --> 42:45.500
Wait. Was I dreaming,
or did you say I was a werewolf?

42:45.600 --> 42:48.300
It's not a joke.

42:48.300 --> 42:51.200
-[ Woman ] I told you this would happen.
-[ Gasps ] Mummy!

42:51.300 --> 42:53.800
- Mummy?
- Leave it to me, please.

42:53.900 --> 42:58.300
You're making the same mistake again.
First Claude, now this.
Can't you be more careful?

42:58.400 --> 43:01.300
- This is different.
Claude stole my blood.
- Hey.

43:01.300 --> 43:03.400
Um, Mrs. Pigot? Um--

43:03.400 --> 43:07.700
Um, I know this looks really kind of--
How do you do?

43:07.800 --> 43:09.900
Uh, I can explain.

43:10.000 --> 43:15.100
It's really not her fault.
Uh, Serafine, could you introduce us?

43:15.100 --> 43:18.500
You wouldn't want to meet me.
I'm not as attractive as I used to be.

43:18.500 --> 43:23.000
Oh, come on.
I bet you two pass for sisters.

43:23.100 --> 43:25.500
Wait a minute.

43:25.600 --> 43:28.900
Hold it. Didn't you say
your mother was dead?

43:29.000 --> 43:32.600
- [ Gasps ]
- [ Mother Screams ]

43:32.600 --> 43:35.200
- You scared her away!
- I scared her?

43:36.200 --> 43:38.200
Ha!
[ Panting ]

43:38.200 --> 43:41.700
That's it.
My friends were right: You're nuts.

43:41.800 --> 43:44.000
Nurses with walking corpses
stealing hearts...

43:44.100 --> 43:47.300
and monsters and werewolves
in the basement and the whole
thing with the thing--

43:47.400 --> 43:50.700
- Andy, let me explain, please.
- No, no. You already did.

43:50.800 --> 43:54.500
I don't know what you dosed me with,
but I will not be the lab rabbit...

43:54.600 --> 43:56.600
for some
psychotic experiment.

43:56.600 --> 43:58.600
[ Jiggling Knob ]

43:58.700 --> 44:03.300
- All right, just stay
away from me. Let me out!
- You must drink this.

44:03.400 --> 44:06.100
- It's the only thing
that will help you.
- Not freakin' likely.

44:06.200 --> 44:08.200
- You should do as she says.
- [ Screaming ]

44:08.300 --> 44:12.300
[ Screaming Continues ]

44:23.700 --> 44:26.800
Andy, hold on!
Andy, hold on! Wait a second!

44:28.100 --> 44:31.100
Where are you going, American?

44:31.200 --> 44:34.100
- [ Muffled Screams ]
- Shh.

44:35.200 --> 44:37.600
I love Americans.

44:56.800 --> 44:59.300
[ Camera Shutter Clicking ]

45:11.200 --> 45:14.000
Hey, vous!
Ne passes pas!

45:18.100 --> 45:20.200
- [ Speaking ln French ]
- No.

45:20.300 --> 45:23.400
- [ Continues ln French ]
- Please, no!

45:28.000 --> 45:30.300
Friend of yours?

45:32.600 --> 45:35.400
I'm lnspector Leduc.
Homicide.

45:49.900 --> 45:52.500
Do you take drugs,
Mr. "Mucdermott"?

45:52.500 --> 45:54.900
It's McDermott.

45:54.900 --> 45:57.800
No, I don't take drugs.

45:57.900 --> 46:00.100
What really happened down there?

46:00.200 --> 46:04.300
Why does almost every corpse
have its heart missing?

46:04.300 --> 46:07.800
Ritual sacrifices?
Are you the member of a sect?

46:07.800 --> 46:12.500
I didn't see.
I was chased... by a big thing.

46:12.600 --> 46:15.200
Um, some kind of wild animal.

46:15.300 --> 46:18.700
Test this man for drugs.

46:23.800 --> 46:25.900
Huh!

46:43.200 --> 46:46.200
[ Bell Tolling ]

46:51.400 --> 46:54.600
[ All Noises lncreasing
ln Decibel ]

46:59.300 --> 47:02.900
[ Chattering ln French Loudly ]

47:04.200 --> 47:07.700
[ Panting, Sniffing Loudly ]

47:14.600 --> 47:17.700
[ Boat Engine Humming Loudly ]

47:17.800 --> 47:21.200
[ Water Bubbling Loudly ]

47:26.700 --> 47:29.700
[ Birds Squawking Loudly ]

47:29.700 --> 47:32.700
[ Dog Panting Loudly ]

47:50.400 --> 47:53.800
## [ Piano, Blues ]

47:57.800 --> 48:00.300
I said rare, bloody.

48:00.400 --> 48:02.300
You understand?

48:02.400 --> 48:04.300
# You know I'm the wolfman #

48:04.400 --> 48:06.500
That'll do...

48:06.600 --> 48:09.000
while I wait.

48:10.600 --> 48:14.100
[ Pager Beeping ]

48:14.200 --> 48:17.300
# You know I'm the wolfman ##

48:27.900 --> 48:30.000
## [ Drums ]

48:39.500 --> 48:41.500
[ Sniffing ]

48:48.800 --> 48:51.600
[ Whimpering, Barking ]

48:51.700 --> 48:53.700
- [ Speaking ln French ]
- Oh, um--

48:53.700 --> 48:57.600
[ Girl ] Hi. Um--
[ Speaking Broken French ]

48:57.700 --> 49:00.400
No. La bottle.

49:00.500 --> 49:03.000
[ Continues Speaking
Broken French ]

49:03.100 --> 49:04.800
[ Barking ]

49:04.900 --> 49:07.600
[ Screams ]

49:07.700 --> 49:10.300
Whoo. Whoa. I'm sorry.

49:10.400 --> 49:12.700
American?

49:14.300 --> 49:16.500
Yeah.

49:16.500 --> 49:19.200
Uh, Andy McDermott.

49:19.300 --> 49:22.600
Amy Finch.

49:22.700 --> 49:27.100
And that's, uh-- [ Sniffs ]
Hot Kitty you're wearing.

49:27.100 --> 49:31.100
- Wow.
- You want some food?

49:33.400 --> 49:35.400
[ Sucking Loudly ]

49:36.900 --> 49:39.200
[ Sucking Loudly ]

49:39.200 --> 49:42.700
[ Sucking Loudly, Giggling ]

49:42.800 --> 49:46.300
- [ Belches ] Excuse me.
- Gar-kon!

49:46.300 --> 49:48.400
- [ Laughs, Hiccups ]
- Monsieur?

49:48.400 --> 49:51.500
- Another bottle
of the "Poo Willy Fwissy".
- Pardon?

49:51.500 --> 49:54.400
- Le hooch de jour.
- [ Amy Giggling ]

49:54.500 --> 49:58.200
I believe it's pronounced
Pouilly Fuisse.

49:58.200 --> 50:00.100
[ Giggles ]

50:04.400 --> 50:06.500
Um, hello.
[ Echoing ]

50:08.400 --> 50:10.800
Are you getting fresh on me?

50:13.500 --> 50:15.700
I'm sorry.

50:15.800 --> 50:20.000
I don't know what's wrong with me.
I'm not normally like this, honest.

50:20.100 --> 50:23.400
[ Laughing, Echoing ]
Right.

50:23.500 --> 50:25.800
No, I'm serious.

50:25.900 --> 50:28.800
The truth is I lost
my best friend today.

50:28.900 --> 50:32.400
[ Laughing ]

50:34.600 --> 50:36.800
- Bon apetit.
- [ Screams ]

50:36.900 --> 50:40.700
You're dead! I saw them
pull you out of the canal!

50:40.800 --> 50:42.700
- No, Monsiuer, the Atlantic.
- [ Laughing ]

50:45.100 --> 50:47.300
Whoa! Get away from me!

50:47.400 --> 50:49.600
Pull yourself together, Andy.
We have to talk.

50:49.600 --> 50:52.800
Talk? Talk!
Wait, you're not real!

50:52.800 --> 50:54.800
All right, let me go!

50:54.800 --> 50:58.500
[ Laughing ]
Did you see--

50:58.600 --> 51:01.900
[ Panting ]

51:09.500 --> 51:12.000
Oh! What do you want?

51:12.100 --> 51:14.400
Oh, sh--

51:14.500 --> 51:16.900
This is a bad dream.

51:17.000 --> 51:20.200
Right? You're not here.

51:20.300 --> 51:24.600
- Are you?
- Andy, you were bitten.

51:24.600 --> 51:27.300
You're already changing.

51:27.400 --> 51:30.200
You would've never looked twice
at that bimbo in there.

51:30.200 --> 51:33.000
All right, I may be upset...

51:33.100 --> 51:37.500
or screwed up right now,
but I'm not a wolf!

51:37.500 --> 51:39.700
Andy, I'm dead serious.

51:39.800 --> 51:42.400
[ Chuckling ]
Dead?

51:42.500 --> 51:46.800
That's funny.
That's really funny.

51:46.900 --> 51:49.900
"Un-dead," actually.

51:49.900 --> 51:52.200
Cursed to walk the earth
as a restless spirit...

51:52.300 --> 51:55.000
till the werewolf
that did me dies.

51:55.100 --> 51:59.000
- What do you want from me?
- What I want from you can wait.

51:59.100 --> 52:02.200
Dump the chick
and lock yourself up.

52:02.300 --> 52:05.000
And do it quick.
The moon's rising.

52:05.100 --> 52:08.800
You're just jealous
'cause I'm about to score.

52:08.800 --> 52:11.400
You know, you can't just pop up
and tell me what to do.

52:11.400 --> 52:14.200
I don't even know
why I'm listening to you.

52:14.300 --> 52:18.600
- I know you're dead
and so do the police.
- [ Zipper Zipping ]

52:24.000 --> 52:27.000
[ Giggling ]

52:27.000 --> 52:29.000
Mmm.

52:29.100 --> 52:34.000
- [ Giggling Resumes ] Ooh, come here.
- [ Bell Tolls ]

52:34.100 --> 52:38.100
Want some? Come here. Ooh.

52:38.100 --> 52:41.600
Hey!
[ Growling ]

52:41.600 --> 52:44.700
The night is young.
The moon is bright.

52:44.800 --> 52:47.300
What do you feel
like doing tonight, tiger?

