Andy?

55:36.900 --> 55:40.900
- [ Screaming ]
- [ Growling ]

55:51.500 --> 55:53.400
[ Growling ]

56:17.200 --> 56:19.100
[ Panting ]

56:22.300 --> 56:25.100
[ Growling, Sniffing ]

56:25.200 --> 56:27.100
[ Roaring ]

56:55.300 --> 56:57.200
[ Hiccups ]

56:59.800 --> 57:02.600
[ Screaming ]

57:04.900 --> 57:08.600
Wait! Stop!
I am policeman.

57:08.600 --> 57:14.000
- [ Gasping ] Oh, thank God.
- [ Barking ]

57:14.000 --> 57:16.700
Oh, you cured my hiccups.

57:16.700 --> 57:18.800
- [ Growling ]
- [ Screaming ]

