[ Dog Barking ]

57:37.300 --> 57:39.800
[ Werewolf Growling ]

57:39.800 --> 57:42.900
[ Dog Whimpering ]

57:44.200 --> 57:46.200
[ Camera Shutters Clicking ]

57:59.800 --> 58:02.900
- Hey, what's goin' on?
- McDermott, you are under arrest.

58:03.000 --> 58:04.900
What for?

58:05.000 --> 58:08.900
The possibilities are limitless.
Take him away.

58:12.900 --> 58:15.700
[ Engine Starts ]

58:15.800 --> 58:17.800
Elle est la.

58:17.800 --> 58:20.500
- Oh, my God.
- That's not all.

58:24.500 --> 58:29.300
- Detective Ben Bou.
I had him follow you.
- This some kind of sick joke?

58:31.000 --> 58:34.200
Wait here a moment.

58:34.300 --> 58:37.500
[ Door Opens, Closes ]

58:47.000 --> 58:49.500
Thanks for a lovely evening,
douche bag.

58:49.500 --> 58:52.800
You really know how to show a girl
a good time, don't you?

58:52.900 --> 58:55.900
No, no, no, no!

58:56.000 --> 58:59.300
- You're dead!
- No! I ain't so lucky. I'm "un-dead."

58:59.400 --> 59:04.800
And as your rotting sidekick,
I am cursed to remain
a restless spirit until you die.

59:04.900 --> 59:07.300
- Not so fast.
- [ Screams ]

59:07.400 --> 59:10.500
If you want my buddy dead,
nut ball, you're gonna have
to wait. I need him first.

59:10.500 --> 59:12.600
He's no use to me
as a corpse.

59:12.700 --> 59:16.800
Spent four years on Stairmaster
to get a package like this.
You ripped it like a lamb chop.

59:16.900 --> 59:19.200
Don't blame me, Andy.
I warned you.

59:19.200 --> 59:22.200
Wait. You mean,
you knew this all along? Oh!

59:23.900 --> 59:26.400
- [ Grunts ]
- Hey, keep it down out there!

59:26.400 --> 59:29.500
A guy can't rest in pieces
around here.

59:29.500 --> 59:34.700
- I'm losing my freaking skull.
- Come on. Pull yourself together, Andy.

59:34.800 --> 59:37.800
You gotta get outta here.
The cops wanna put you away for life.

59:37.900 --> 59:41.700
I've had enough of your ridiculous
theories. The man is dangerous.

59:43.500 --> 59:46.500
Lock him up!

59:47.900 --> 59:49.900
McDermott, you're--

59:51.600 --> 59:54.300
I didn't choose
to become a werewolf.

59:54.400 --> 59:56.900
I can't face eating people
the rest of my life.

59:56.900 --> 59:58.800
Better get used to it.

59:58.900 --> 01:00:02.600
Isn't there any way that
I can become human again?

01:00:02.700 --> 01:00:07.400
Yeah, there is,
but you're not gonna like it.

01:00:07.500 --> 01:00:09.600
Tell me. How?

01:00:09.700 --> 01:00:13.400
First, find the werewolf
that bit you.

01:00:13.400 --> 01:00:15.900
Then kill it.

01:00:15.900 --> 01:00:19.000
Then eat out its heart.

01:00:19.100 --> 01:00:21.000
What?

01:00:21.100 --> 01:00:23.200
But that means--

01:00:24.700 --> 01:00:26.900
Serafine?

01:00:27.000 --> 01:00:29.800
I-- No way.

01:00:29.900 --> 01:00:32.000
- Andy, look out!
- [ Bus Horn Honking ]

01:00:35.100 --> 01:00:37.900
- What did you do that for?
- 'Cause I still need him.

01:00:38.000 --> 01:00:41.400
- He's gonna help kill the guy
who did this to me.
- I feel sick.

01:00:41.500 --> 01:00:44.800
All of this would be over right now
if you hadn't opened your fat trap.

01:00:44.800 --> 01:00:46.600
You are the most egocentric corpse
I've ever met.

01:00:46.700 --> 01:00:51.200
Listen, I don't know what kind
of friend this jerk is to you,
but he ate my spleen.

01:00:55.000 --> 01:00:58.100
So, hey. You guys
are werewolves too, huh?

01:00:58.100 --> 01:01:00.800
Super.

01:01:00.800 --> 01:01:03.600
- Glad to know ya.
- Andy.

01:01:03.700 --> 01:01:07.500
I don't think you have accepted the gift
that has been given to you...

01:01:07.500 --> 01:01:10.200
or much less appreciated it.

01:01:21.700 --> 01:01:24.600
[ Claude ] We have a mission, Andy:
to purify the world.

01:01:26.400 --> 01:01:29.300
That's why we pick our victims
from the scum of society.

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:36.300
The governments of the world
spent billions on medicine,

01:01:36.400 --> 01:01:39.100
welfare, charity.

01:01:39.200 --> 01:01:41.100
To what effect?

01:01:41.200 --> 01:01:44.400
It only keeps alive
the weak, the stupid, the lazy,

01:01:44.500 --> 01:01:48.200
who breed and multiply,
weakening the human race.

01:01:48.300 --> 01:01:50.400
All my men, I have chosen...

01:01:50.500 --> 01:01:53.900
for their loyalty,
their dedication to the coming age.

01:01:53.900 --> 01:01:56.600
But you--

01:01:57.900 --> 01:02:00.100
You were not
to have been.

01:02:02.700 --> 01:02:06.800
You were an accident,
an anomaly.

01:02:06.900 --> 01:02:09.800
I do not wish to kill you.

01:02:09.900 --> 01:02:15.100
I pray you will join us in our rise
to become the new mankind.

01:02:15.200 --> 01:02:18.000
Pure, free of disease.

01:02:18.100 --> 01:02:20.900
Free from the trappings
of technological advance.

01:02:23.000 --> 01:02:26.400
Will you join us, Andy?

01:02:27.900 --> 01:02:30.800
I don't know. That's, you know--
That's a big decision.

01:02:30.900 --> 01:02:35.400
- Mm-hmm.
- I'm gonna need some time
to think about that.

01:02:35.500 --> 01:02:37.600
Sure.

01:02:45.400 --> 01:02:48.100
[ Gasping ]
Andy?

01:02:52.300 --> 01:02:56.000
- Well, what's that for?
- Kill him, Andy.

01:02:56.100 --> 01:02:58.400
[ Claude ]
Cut out his heart.

01:03:01.400 --> 01:03:03.800
Wait. Couldn't we just--
[ Sighs ]

01:03:10.300 --> 01:03:13.400
Release him, Andy.

01:03:23.200 --> 01:03:25.500
Join us.

01:03:29.000 --> 01:03:31.600
You can't ask me to do this.

01:03:33.700 --> 01:03:37.300
- Join us.
- I'd rather die.

01:03:37.300 --> 01:03:40.000
And so you shall.

01:04:03.200 --> 01:04:06.100
[ Serafine ]
Andy!

01:04:06.200 --> 01:04:08.100
Serafine!

01:04:23.700 --> 01:04:25.600
Down there.

01:04:28.100 --> 01:04:30.100
Keep going.

01:04:53.200 --> 01:04:55.700
- Jump!
- But Chris--

01:04:55.800 --> 01:04:57.600
Jump!

01:04:57.700 --> 01:05:01.100
[ Screams ]

01:05:16.500 --> 01:05:19.600
Follow me.

01:05:31.600 --> 01:05:33.500
[ Pounding ]

01:05:51.100 --> 01:05:53.400
[ Panting ]

01:05:54.700 --> 01:05:57.200
- What?
- Did you know?

01:05:57.300 --> 01:05:59.800
- What is it?
- Did you know what he plans to do?

01:05:59.800 --> 01:06:03.600
- [ Sighs ] Yes, I did.
- And you did nothing to stop him?

01:06:03.600 --> 01:06:06.500
- Andy, l--
- How in God's name could you
just stand by--

01:06:06.600 --> 01:06:10.600
For God's sake! Stop it!
We may have a cure.

01:06:14.200 --> 01:06:17.000
Thierry, my stepfather.

01:06:20.400 --> 01:06:22.300
- Claude?
- No.

01:06:22.400 --> 01:06:24.600
You?

01:06:24.700 --> 01:06:27.600
And my mother too.

01:06:27.700 --> 01:06:31.000
For a time, I had managed
not to harm anyone.

01:06:31.000 --> 01:06:34.600
Even the hearts my mother smuggled
from the hospital were from the dead.

01:06:34.700 --> 01:06:38.100
Two months ago,
he was sure he had discovered...

01:06:38.200 --> 01:06:41.600
a serum to suppress
my lycanthropic cycle.

01:06:41.700 --> 01:06:43.600
Only it had
the reverse effect.

01:06:43.700 --> 01:06:46.100
I immediately transformed.

01:06:48.700 --> 01:06:51.600
My mother heard the noise
from upstairs,

01:06:51.600 --> 01:06:54.800
and Thierry tried to escape
through the underground.

01:06:59.300 --> 01:07:01.700
When I came to,

01:07:01.800 --> 01:07:04.000
I saw I had butchered
my own parents.

01:07:06.000 --> 01:07:08.700
Now do you see why
I was trying to kill myself?

01:07:08.800 --> 01:07:10.900
It's not your fault.

01:07:16.300 --> 01:07:19.900
Don't worry about me.
It's Chris who has problems.

01:07:20.000 --> 01:07:22.700
We gotta get him
out of there.

01:07:22.800 --> 01:07:26.200
[ Gasps ]

01:07:26.300 --> 01:07:28.200
Claude is a bastard.

01:07:47.300 --> 01:07:50.500
[ Car Brakes Screeching ]

01:07:50.600 --> 01:07:53.000
Oh, brother, just who I need.

01:07:53.100 --> 01:07:58.200
## [ Rock, lndistinct ]

01:08:02.100 --> 01:08:04.200
Check the cellar!

01:08:08.300 --> 01:08:11.200
Leave him alone, Claude.

01:08:11.300 --> 01:08:14.100
- Out the back! Quick!
- [ Screaming ]

01:08:14.100 --> 01:08:18.000
I warn you.
Don't interfere again.

01:08:18.000 --> 01:08:21.800
# I am revved up
See him fall into the trees #

