Yoo-hoo!
He's over here!

01:08:42.600 --> 01:08:44.700
Cut it out.

01:08:49.399 --> 01:08:52.200
- [ Grumbles ]
- Hey, he's hiding by the car!

01:08:52.300 --> 01:08:55.000
- Qu'est-ce qui se passe la?
- He-- He's getting away!

01:08:55.100 --> 01:08:57.000
Fools! Get over here!

01:08:57.100 --> 01:09:00.600
- Ah, c'est toi, le chauffeur!
- I say, steady on, old man.
I never touched your car.

01:09:00.700 --> 01:09:03.100
[ Shouting ln French ]

01:09:06.800 --> 01:09:09.899
[ Gasps ]
Oh, oh. Great.

01:09:12.899 --> 01:09:15.899
- [ Speaking French ]
- [ Yelling ln French ]

01:09:34.700 --> 01:09:37.800
## [ Rock, lndistinct ]

