- [ Beeping ]
- [ Serafine Gasping ]

01:10:07.700 --> 01:10:09.700
[ Beeping Continues ]

01:10:12.700 --> 01:10:15.300
- Sera--
- Hurry up!

01:10:16.900 --> 01:10:18.800
[ Beeping Continues ]

01:10:18.900 --> 01:10:21.300
- [ Panting]
- Serafine.

01:10:21.400 --> 01:10:26.000
[ Crying ]
The cure. If he dies, we have no hope.

01:10:26.100 --> 01:10:28.300
Serafine, it's--
He's gone.

01:10:28.400 --> 01:10:30.500
Let it go.

01:10:30.600 --> 01:10:32.600
- No.
- Yes.

01:10:32.600 --> 01:10:35.000
[ Crying ]

01:10:35.100 --> 01:10:37.400
They killed him,
the bastards.

01:10:37.500 --> 01:10:39.400
[ Sniffling ]

01:10:39.500 --> 01:10:41.700
What do we do now?

01:10:41.800 --> 01:10:43.700
Well, let me have a shot at it.

01:10:43.800 --> 01:10:49.300
But they ruined the lab.
So many years of hard work.

01:10:49.400 --> 01:10:51.400
Did your stepfather leave any notes?

01:10:51.400 --> 01:10:54.200
There.

01:10:57.900 --> 01:10:59.800
What does that represent?

01:10:59.900 --> 01:11:02.500
A werewolf's biorhythm...

01:11:02.500 --> 01:11:05.700
and how it's governed
by the cycles of the moon.

01:11:05.800 --> 01:11:08.600
Thierry tried to keep me below
the transformation threshold...

01:11:08.600 --> 01:11:11.900
by injecting me with a depressant.

01:11:12.000 --> 01:11:14.000
And it had a reverse effect.

01:11:14.100 --> 01:11:17.000
- Yeah.
- All right.

01:11:17.100 --> 01:11:19.900
Just so I'm totally clear here,
with this drug,

01:11:20.000 --> 01:11:23.600
you can induce a transformation
at any time of the month?

01:11:23.700 --> 01:11:26.700
Oh, my God. The samples.
He left them in the cupboard.

01:11:26.700 --> 01:11:28.700
Over there.

01:11:32.800 --> 01:11:34.400
Mon Dieu.

01:11:44.100 --> 01:11:46.900
Oh, brother.

01:11:47.000 --> 01:11:49.000
## [ Rock ]

01:11:57.200 --> 01:11:59.100
Good luck.

