# Wild
I should've kept you out #

01:12:51.500 --> 01:12:55.700
## [ Continues ]

01:13:08.500 --> 01:13:11.300
- [ Music Stops ]
- [ Crowd Moaning ]

01:13:11.300 --> 01:13:14.100
