Arrest that man!

01:13:14.200 --> 01:13:16.500
Listen to me!
It's important!

01:13:16.600 --> 01:13:20.600
You're all in great danger!
You have to leave the building now!

01:13:20.700 --> 01:13:24.600
It's a trap!
I'm serious!

01:13:29.500 --> 01:13:31.600
Please, listen to me!

01:13:31.700 --> 01:13:36.200
- [ Man ] No!
- Skinheads are planning a massacre!

01:13:40.900 --> 01:13:43.400
No! Stop!

01:13:45.700 --> 01:13:48.000
- You have to leave the building!
- [ Crowd Booing ]

01:13:51.100 --> 01:13:55.100
- All right, all right, all right.
All right.
- [ Crowd Cheering ]

01:13:58.200 --> 01:14:01.200
[ Chanting ]

01:14:33.500 --> 01:14:35.800
- Hey! Hey!
- Hey! Open that door!

01:14:38.200 --> 01:14:42.700
Welcome, Americans,
to our lndependence party!

01:14:42.800 --> 01:14:45.600
[ Cheering ]

01:14:47.500 --> 01:14:51.900
I love you, Americans!

01:14:51.900 --> 01:14:55.100
What great taste you have.

01:14:56.900 --> 01:15:00.800
[ Claude ]
Every man on the planet...

01:15:00.800 --> 01:15:04.800
must take every opportunity
to show his gratitude.

01:15:04.800 --> 01:15:09.100
Because you share your culture
and resolutions with the whole world,

01:15:09.200 --> 01:15:12.700
spreading it
to all other nations,

01:15:12.700 --> 01:15:15.500
influencing all other cultures...

01:15:19.500 --> 01:15:23.000
and touching the hearts
of millions.

01:15:24.500 --> 01:15:28.500
Now I wish to share something...
with you.

01:15:28.500 --> 01:15:32.200
I dedicate this party
to all you Americans,

01:15:32.200 --> 01:15:35.300
whose heart I wish to touch
in return.

01:15:36.500 --> 01:15:38.500
- Let the show begin.
- [ Cheering ]

01:15:38.500 --> 01:15:41.300
## [ Rock ]

01:15:45.500 --> 01:15:48.400
Chris!

01:15:48.500 --> 01:15:51.700
[ Gunshots ]

01:15:54.300 --> 01:15:56.800
- Stop them! Stop them!
- Enough!

01:15:56.900 --> 01:16:00.200
- Stop them!
- You are all under arrest!

01:16:00.300 --> 01:16:02.600
The party is over!

01:16:02.700 --> 01:16:05.600
Everybody else, go home!

01:16:17.400 --> 01:16:19.100
Inspector!

01:16:19.200 --> 01:16:22.800
## [ Continues ]

01:16:25.000 --> 01:16:27.700
## [ Continues ]

01:16:27.700 --> 01:16:30.600
Come on. Come on!

01:16:30.700 --> 01:16:33.000
Come on. Move. Move!

01:16:33.100 --> 01:16:35.800
[ Grunting ]

01:16:37.400 --> 01:16:39.300
Allez! Quoi?

01:16:43.000 --> 01:16:44.900
## [ Stops ]

01:16:46.100 --> 01:16:49.000
[ Screaming ]

01:16:50.900 --> 01:16:54.400
[ Werewolf Panting, Growling ]

01:17:09.900 --> 01:17:13.100
Send for reinforcements!
We got a massacre!

01:17:15.300 --> 01:17:18.400
Stop or I'll shoot!

01:17:18.400 --> 01:17:21.200
[ Gunfire ]

01:17:51.900 --> 01:17:53.400
[ Engine Starts ]

01:18:19.500 --> 01:18:22.100
[ Screaming ]

01:18:35.500 --> 01:18:37.700
Allez-y!

01:18:37.800 --> 01:18:42.200
[ Crowd Shouting ]

01:18:46.700 --> 01:18:50.000
- Serafine!
- [ Growling ]

01:18:51.600 --> 01:18:54.400
[ Shrieking ]

01:19:00.900 --> 01:19:02.900
I'll show you.

01:19:04.400 --> 01:19:07.100
Claude went down
that trap door.

01:19:07.200 --> 01:19:10.100
It's true. Look.
Huge creatures covered in hair. Look.

01:19:10.200 --> 01:19:12.800
Huh? That's impossible.

01:19:12.900 --> 01:19:16.100
Just what I said... drugs.

01:19:16.200 --> 01:19:20.000
